Christian Romer
Dubai, United Arab Emirates229 contributions
Beautiful buildings
Feb 2023
These towers are a Dubai institution. Wonderful architecture, inside and out. One tower consists of mainly offices, whereas the other is a hotel owned by Jumeirah. There are also a few standalone restaurants in the middle. The area is beautiful - you can walk from DIFC (Dubai International Financial Centre) and make your way around the Emirates Towers and the Museum of the Future. If you’re lucky, you may see some roaming peacocks as well!
Written June 7, 2023
